paint.shared.objects

Class Recording

  • java.lang.Object
    • paint.shared.objects.Recording

  • public class Recording
extends Object
    Represents metadata and associated analysis data for a specific recording within an experiment. This class includes measurement metrics, analysis parameters, and relationships to Square and Track objects.

      • Recording

        public Recording(String experimentName,
                 String recordingName,
                 int conditionNumber,
                 int replicateNumber,
                 String probeName,
                 String probeType,
                 String cellType,
                 String adjuvant,
                 double concentration,
                 boolean processFlag,
                 double threshold)
        Creates a Recording initialized with its basic metadata.
        Parameters:
        experimentName - the experiment name
        recordingName - the recording identifier
        conditionNumber - the condition number
        replicateNumber - the replicate number
        probeName - the probe name
        probeType - the probe type (e.g., dye, antibody)
        cellType - the cell type
        adjuvant - the adjuvant, if any
        concentration - the probe/treatment concentration
        processFlag - whether this recording should be processed
        threshold - threshold value for analysis
